{"tid":2163891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"早建數據庫掌管公民  專制長臂伸向全球","createTime":"2020-08-19T02:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T02:27:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4feb5d31ccaf15e3585356a3ecad4f079bbcbc0b","tid":2163891,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T02:27:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200819/AOQM5VI7EZECVCSOP4PF7N4HPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200819%2FAOQM5VI7EZECVCSOP4PF7N4HPQ%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5iNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=57cd9171\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200819%2FAOQM5VI7EZECVCSOP4PF7N4HPQ%2F&h=b397be45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200819/AOQM5VI7EZECVCSOP4PF7N4HPQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n早建數據庫掌管公民 <br />\n專制長臂伸向全球<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lzfM3aPk1P0MMUVrtW0RbpjJSa0=/1098x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VLK6ETMAGJBF5NQG5OO644Q2OU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlzfM3aPk1P0MMUVrtW0RbpjJSa0%3D%2F1098x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVLK6ETMAGJBF5NQG5OO644Q2OU.jpg&h=d87af3d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■潘永忠（田牧）於新書發佈會中表示，封殺言論及新聞自由，就不能緩解民憤壓力，隨時有爆炸的可能。<br />\n<br />\n「因特網（internet）是上天送給中國人的禮物，民眾可以利用它發表意見，吐露心聲。」獨立中文筆會會長副秘書長潘永忠（筆名田牧）對本報引述該會前會長劉曉波曾這樣說。潘永忠指中共網絡審查自上世紀90年代末已開始，「網絡審查與監控是中共專制的本質」，而這種本質也隨着中國的社交媒體軟件在國際走紅而發揮影響力，儼如中國「審查的長臂」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lx3Uoe1GtW_IbiHskNFk_fpQKfM=/1330x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V3MWU6XLPJALBBDKYKTKIMMWQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Flx3Uoe1GtW_IbiHskNFk_fpQKfM%3D%2F1330x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV3MWU6XLPJALBBDKYKTKIMMWQA.jpg&h=87b8be0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國阿富汗裔女學生Feroza Aziz在TikTok中邊分享化妝教學，邊討論新疆集中營的影片，被TikTok封鎖賬號。<br />\n<br />\n潘永忠一直研究中國媒體和互聯網生態，著有《走進中國新聞出版審查禁地》一書。他說，追本溯源，當大家想着互聯網可以為人類造福，中共就「早着先機」，「1998年，中國公安部開始建設。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國外言論不倖免<br />\n<br />\n「中共的陰影無所不在，不僅在自己的網絡工具中，就是國外的網絡工具中，也同樣的實行審查與監控。」潘永忠直指，中國的審查延伸至國際並非不能想像的事。TikTok等被美。。。。。。。。。"}]}